I recently fired my web developer, and am searching for a new one or two that can work together. (really only need one though) Anyway, get in contact with me if you’re interested and you must be a half decent web developer, and have a moderate amount of experience. I’m not expecting some super professional even though that’d be great. Get ahold of me via skype;

im2high2behere
